summary: This document is an appraisal report for a residential property located at 9 East 71st Street, New York, NY, commissioned by the Federal Bureau of Investigation. The appraisal, conducted by Gary D. Lane, estimates the market value of the property at $86,250,000 as of July 13, 2019, based on a limited exterior inspection and comparative market analysis.

keyFacts: The appraised value of the property at 9 East 71st Street is estimated at $86,250,000 as of July 13, 2019.
The appraisal was conducted by Gary D. Lane, who performed an exterior-only inspection.
The report includes comparisons to three other properties sold in the area, with sale prices ranging from $39,000,000 to $77,100,000.
The appraisal report is restricted for the sole use of the Federal Bureau of Investigation.
The appraiser assumes no responsibility for the interior condition of the property, as the appraisal was based solely on exterior observations.
